OL,3,C'This is really unfair': King's Cross
OL,4,Cremoves train information early
OL,6,FRail bosses have been removing trains
OL,7,Ffrom departure boards three minutes
OL,8,Fbefore they leave to prevent
OL,9,Fpassengers from rushing to stations.
OL,10,FNetwork Rail is trialling this
OL,11,Ftechnique to ensure everyone can board
OL,12,Fsafely and keep the trains running on
OL,13,Ftime.
OL,15,FAt London's King's Cross station,
OL,16,FNetwork Rail will introduce new times
OL,17,Ffor the last tannoy announcement,
OL,18,Fwhich will be read out just four
OL,19,Fminutes before long-distance trains
OL,20,Fdepart.
