OL,3,C'This is really unfair': King's Cross
OL,4,Cremoves train information early
OL,6,FPosters warning commuters about the
OL,7,Fchanges have been circulating in the
OL,8,Fbusy station. Still, they have sparked
OL,9,Fcontroversy on social media as many
OL,10,Fcommuters express concerns about
OL,11,Fpotentially missing their trains.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV London, Travel expert
OL,14,FSimon Calder said "This is really
OL,15,Funfair. Passengers should be the judge
OL,16,Fof whether they can make it on time,
OL,17,Fnot Network Rail.
