OL,3,C'This is really unfair': King's Cross
OL,4,Cremoves train information early
OL,6,FA Network Rail spokesperson said "Our
OL,7,Fstations plan their announcements to
OL,8,Fgive passengers the safest and easiest
OL,9,Fstart to their journeys and to make
OL,10,Fsure trains can depart on time.
OL,12,F"At King's Cross, we display long-
OL,13,Fdistance trains on the main departure
OL,14,Fboards until three minutes before
OL,15,Fdeparture, and this has been normal
OL,16,Fpractice for some time.
