OL,3,C'This is really unfair': King's Cross
OL,4,Cremoves train information early
OL,6,F"The trial will just see the last
OL,7,Ftannoy announcements being made four
OL,8,Fminutes before departure on long-
OL,9,Fdistance trains to give people plenty
OL,10,Fof time to get to their trains. There
OL,11,Fis no change being made to actual
OL,12,Fboarding times, and passengers can
OL,13,Fstill board their train up to 20
OL,14,Fminutes before departure, as is the
OL,15,Fnormal process."
